  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Advancing the FC-G5S civilian harm mitigation in the Sahel</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">During a two-year period of implementation, CIVIC will support the FC-G5S to deploy and fully operationalize the MISAD at the PCIAT, Fuseaux, and battalions levels across the force. A critical element of this will be the FC-G5S efforts to standardize its responses to incidents of civilian harm, both to respond to victims through post-harm amends, and how it integrates that learning into future operations to mitigate such instances occurring in the future.</narrative>
  </description>
